room_title: Escape room "Time To Die" by Break Out! in Cedar Rapids
review: This was so much fun! We did "Time to Die" and survived with :53 seconds left!!! It was pretty awesome, and I really enjoyed doing this with my fam!! Will definitely do this again!

room_title: Escape room "Time To Die" by Break Out! in Cedar Rapids
review: We have done two rooms for a team-building event. Taken was a cool room and very tame with the decorations. Just did Time to Die today - it was awesome! Just being told one person had to be handcuffed to the wall and we all had to go in with blindfolds on made it that much more intense! And we broke out! Definitely would recommend.
